snippet.title: Magic: Legends | Cinematic Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Announcing - Magic: Legends!
A thrilling online Action RPG set across the iconic planes of Magic: The Gathering! In Magic: Legends, become immersed in the acclaimed fictional Magic multiverse as a powerful, spell-wielding Planeswalker.

Sign up for Beta, exclusive content, and more at http://www.PlayMagicLegends.com.

Like: https://www.facebook.com/BeAMagicLegend
Follow: https://twitter.com/BeAMagicLegend
Watch: http://www.twitch.tv/BeAMagicLegend
